Description: Implements a unified framework of parametric simplex method for
    a variety of sparse learning problems (e.g., Dantzig selector for linear
    regression, sparse quantile regression, sparse support vector machines,
    and compressive sensing) combined with efficient hyper-parameter selection
    strategies. The core algorithm is implemented in C++ with 'Eigen' support
    for portable high performance linear algebra.
Imports: Matrix
LinkingTo: RcppEigen
